data.description: BUYERS FINANCING FELL THROUGH! This is it! Home sits on .36 acre corner lot, great for a pool and still have plenty of room in the backyard for the kids and entertaining. Work from home? No problem! Study with French doors, off of the living room that has wood burning fireplace. Kitchen has plenty of custom cabinets, granite counter tops. with a walk in pantry. Eat in kitchen. Split bedrooms. Master bedroom looks out over the backyard, and the bath has a jetted garden tub to soak in after a long day. Standing shower, double vanity with linen closet. Check out the size of the walk in closet that has a built in dresser. Home is in the desirable High Point Estates. Close to schools, restaurants, Lake Ray Roberts, Jordan Park, the downtown square, fifteen minutes to the Tollway, hour from the DFW Airport. This home offers private tours and virtual tours. Reach out and set an appointment to view!!Foundation and Plumbing have been done on the property.
